                If you would like to review your order summary, you can <a asp-page="/Orderhistory/BookATimeOrderHistory"> click here </a> to access your account and view the details. <br /> <br />

                I look forward to our upcoming meeting and to welcoming you and your dog. Thank you for choosing me to take care of your dog's well-being. <br /> <br />

                Kind regards, <br /> <br />

                Krisztina <br />
                Phone: +45 29 25 25 38 & Email: shampoodledk@gmail.com <br />
                Shampoodle
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
